      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "'I'll take it' (Making a decision)",
          "arabic": "'سآخذه' (اتخاذ قرار)"
        },
        "text": "Once you've decided to buy, you can say 'nakhdha' (I'll take it, feminine) or 'nakhdhu' (I'll take it, masculine). The 'ha' or 'hu' refers to the item.",
